item.title: 317 Help with ::empty command TORVAPKZ
item.dc:creator: @RyRyscape RyRyscape
item.description:
@RyRyscape wrote:

Place this in commands.java with all the other commands. If you want it for players, paste in where all the other player commands are. Same goes if you just want it for admin+ if (playerCommand.equalsIgnoreCase("empty")) { c.getPA().removeAllItems(); }

If you still don’t know where to put it, I won’t tell you. I already spoonfed you :P.
